    30Рєњ## Using `mdbook` as a library
    32РєњThe `mdbook` binary is just a wrapper around the underlying mdBook crates,
    33Рєњexposing their functionality as a command-line program. If you want to
    34Рєњprogrammatically drive mdBook, you can use the [`mdbook-driver`] crate.
